Prerequisites:
	- Django 1.2
	- Python 2.5
	- vobject — http://pypi.python.org/pypi/vobject
    - django-cal
      -> git://github.com/gabrielgrant/django-cal.git
	- django-social-auth
	  -> django-openid-auth
    - django-piston 0.2.2
	- South — http://pypi.python.org/pypi/South
	
Copy settings.default.py to settings.py and change the db settings

On the first run (or when models are heavily changed):
	python manage.py syncdb
	python manage.py migrate hat	

Afterwards:
	python manage.py runserver
	
The app will be running on http://localhost:8000

Admin console: http://your-host/admin
